text: Estadio Libertador General San Martín is the football (soccer) venue of the Atlético Club San Martín of the Mendoza Province in Argentina. Inaugurated on April 1, 1956, it accommodates 12,000 spectators. Its field measures 70m x 100m. The stadium holds a parking lot, a laundry, a kitchen, restaurant, conference room and sanitary services. ==External links== *Stadium information Category:Football venues in Argentina
title: Estadio San Martín
